{"tid":2113451,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"速報：三浦春馬自殺身亡 得年30歲","createTime":"2020-07-18T06:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T23:29:31.000Z","uid":231886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2c100b3428944dbfd3aa1155eca04683591dab","tid":2113451,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"根據日本傳媒的新聞消息，明星三浦春馬被發現於其港區住所死亡，初步判斷為自殺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/news24ntv/status/1284369855102119936?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnews24ntv%2Fstatus%2F1284369855102119936%3Fs%3D20&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=c2567b44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnews24ntv%2Fstatus%2F1284369855102119936%3Fs%3D20&h=02e16186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/news24ntv/status/1284369855102119936?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據消息人士指，三浦當日是有工作預定，但卻沒有依時出現，關係人士於是前往其住所，最終於日本時間7月18日13:00左右，上吊身亡的三浦春馬於其港區住所內被發現，送院後證實死亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFLRw29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFLRw29.jpg&h=39d2e99c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32e746f1e6357f0964b564572fe897d5c674f0c1","tid":2113451,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"下？！"},{"pid":"574b28aea3841728bdcf7b710c0c2e4c5fbd9e57","tid":2113451,"uid":118675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"上吊？"},{"pid":"3ab24a433f85b39ff45915e3183f1eee86e24130","tid":2113451,"uid":67050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"唔係卦"},{"pid":"ef16ed52fbe8488760b21e03932ea83d9d7e44cc","tid":2113451,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689d3c4c75d6f47f80128742fda07fe15c5a1fb4","tid":211345